title: Jessica Hagy: How to Be Interesting, Go Viral, & Have The Coolest Job Ever
itunes:author: John Bonini
itunes:summary: Jessica Hagy is an artist and writer best known for her award-winning blog, Indexed. In this casual chat, Hagy discusses how she went viral, quit her job in advertising at Victoria Secret, and now has the coolest job ever.
